  Else
   Raz [M]WCLCDOC,[M]WCLCLIB
   Grizo [M]WCLCDOC
  Endif
  Affzo [M]WCLCDOC,WCLCLIB
Endif
Return
# END SEGAY 18/01/13 US 1231 81085
